lead_paragraph: Manchester City striker Sergio Aguero is back to his lethal best, manager Manuel Pellegrini said on Wednesday after the Argentine's brilliant header booked his side's place in the League Cup final.

headline.print_headline: Lethal Weapon Aguero Back to His Best, Says Pellegrini
